---
// KOL vs KOC Comparison Section Component
---

<section class="container comparison-section" style="padding: 60px 24px;">
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <span class="badge" style="background: #000; color: #fff; border:none; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.75rem;">Industry Shift</span>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #000;">Traditional KOLs are dying. <br>Long live the Consumer.</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 600px;">Mengapa brand global beralih dari satu "Mega Influencer" ke ribuan "Micro Voices".</p>
    </div>

    <div class="editorial-comparison">
        <!-- Row 1: Audience -->
        <div class="compare-row-edit">
            <div class="metric-label">Jumlah Audiens</div>
            <div class="old-way">
                <span class="cross-label">KOL (Leader)</span>
                <div class="val-text">Massif / Besar</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Fokus pada jangkauan luas tapi kurang spesifik.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="new-way">
                <span class="check-label">KOC (Consumer)</span>
                <div class="val-text">Niche / Menengah</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Target audiens spesifik dan sangat loyal.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Row 2: Best For -->
        <div class="compare-row-edit">
            <div class="metric-label">Paling Cocok Untuk</div>
            <div class="old-way">
                <span class="cross-label">KOL</span>
                <div class="val-text">Brand Awareness</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Peluncuran produk baru ke pasar luas.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="new-way">
                <span class="check-label">KOC</span>
                <div class="val-text">Review & Trust</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Membangun kepercayaan dan konversi penjualan.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Row 3: Cost -->
        <div class="compare-row-edit">
            <div class="metric-label">Biaya</div>
            <div class="old-way">
                <span class="cross-label">KOL</span>
                <div class="val-text">Sangat Tinggi</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Mahal untuk satu kali posting.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="new-way">
                <span class="check-label">KOC</span>
                <div class="val-text">Rendah - Sedang</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Sangat efisien, bisa dapat banyak konten sekaligus.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Row 4: Credibility -->
        <div class="compare-row-edit">
            <div class="metric-label">Kredibilitas</div>
            <div class="old-way">
                <span class="cross-label">KOL</span>
                <div class="val-text">Rendah / Bias</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Sering dianggap "Iklan Berbayar" (Hard Selling).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="new-way">
                <span class="check-label">KOC</span>
                <div class="val-text">Sangat Tinggi</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Audiens lebih percaya review dari sesama konsumen.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

         <!-- Row 5: Influence Type -->
         <div class="compare-row-edit">
            <div class="metric-label">Tipe Pengaruh</div>
            <div class="old-way">
                <span class="cross-label">KOL</span>
                <div class="val-text">Otoritas (Fans)</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Hubungan Idola ke Fans (Satu Arah).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="new-way">
                <span class="check-label">KOC</span>
                <div class="val-text">Peer-to-Peer (Teman)</div>
                <div class="val-sub">Hubungan setara seperti rekomendasi teman (Dua Arah).</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .editorial-comparison {
        border-top: 1px solid #000;
        margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .compare-row-edit {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
        padding: 16px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .metric-label {
        font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        padding: 4px 8px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        width: fit-content;
        color: #000;
        line-height: 1;
    }
    
    .old-way { opacity: 0.7; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
    .old-way:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
    
    .new-way { position: relative; }

    .cross-label, .check-label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .cross-label { color: #DC2626; }
    .check-label { color: var(--success-green); }

    .val-text {
        font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .new-way .val-text {
        color: #000;
    }
    .new-way .val-sub {
        color: #242220; /* Solid dark text for KOC */
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    .val-sub {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .compare-row-edit { 
            grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
            gap: 12px; 
            padding: 12px 0; 
        }
        .metric-label { margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .val-text { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    }
</style>
